      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEORGE ALEXIS (1) was below latest but prior to that a Restricted WIN winner in quick time (23.58) at this track in a Restricted WIN. Better than latest and can atone here. ZIPPING KORDA (2) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (23.87) at this track over 407m. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Ready to find winning form. LONE HUNTER (3) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 4.5 lengths into third (29.99) at this track in a OPEN over 510m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. APOLLO'S SUN (7) was a huge winner last start. Big chance on that form.",
